gemorna-nutshell — non-commercial research license
====================================================

The gemorna-nutshell pipeline wraps and bundles two upstream tools whose
licenses restrict commercial use and/or redistribution:

  • GEMORNA   (RainaBio)        — non-commercial research only
  • LinearFold (Huang Lab, OSU) — no redistribution for a fee

Because gemorna-nutshell is a derivative work of these tools and reproduces
their assets (model checkpoints, vocabulary, source code via Apptainer image),
the COMPOSITE work — including the wrapper code in this repository — inherits
their combined restrictions. The text of each upstream license is reproduced
verbatim in THIRD_PARTY_LICENSES.md and must travel with any copy of this
repository or its build artefacts (.sif image, Docker image, etc.).

In particular, by accessing, downloading, or using this pipeline you agree:

  1. To use it solely for non-commercial research purposes (per GEMORNA).
  2. Not to redistribute it (or any derivative work) to third parties for a
     fee, except as necessary to publish academic research in accordance with
     standard academic practice.
  3. To retain this LICENSE file and THIRD_PARTY_LICENSES.md in every copy
     and modification.
  4. To cite the upstream tools (GEMORNA paper, LinearFold paper) in any
     academic work that uses results produced by this pipeline.

For commercial use, contact the GEMORNA corresponding author
(caojicong@rainabio.com) and the LinearFold corresponding author
(liang.huang.sh@gmail.com) to obtain separate commercial licenses.

